/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66b41d525b2c8666032f6ae4468007fc302a588","tid":1540481,"uid":12929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"60d3ac0ef61f5b42ecc79c1bb6078a37cb46f9d0","tid":1540481,"uid":313646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:14:14.000Z","msg":"真心好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:01:39.000Z","msg":"香港人一定要識唱呢幾首兒歌<br />\n<br />\n坐地鐵塞車既時候可以唱，鳩嗚又可以唱<br />\n<br />\n任何時候都可以唱<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以幫手整成YouTube 歌<br />\n<br />\n要形成全城反暴警既社會風氣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【虐殺市民】（聖誕老人）<br />\n<br />\n虐殺市民 終身監禁<br />\n陀住支槍去殺人<br />\n見到令妹 起勢卜棍<br />\n賭波飲茶 實幫襯<br />\n<br />\n【有班警察毅進仔】（有隻雀仔跌落水）<br />\n<br />\n有班警察毅進仔<br />\n人又廢 又要威<br />\n有班警察位置低<br />\n做狗乞米<br />\n<br />\n老母知你做隻龜<br />\n流淚涕 忤逆仔<br />\n想塞返你入個西<br />\n唔畀出世<br />\n<br />\n老公加班腎也虧<br />\n無力砌　悶過閪<br />\n約班SP大隻仔<br />\n綠帽襟計<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【警犬故事】（警察故事）<br />\n<br />\n無自信 毅進仔<br />\n射砲博出位<br />\n人又廢 做隻龜<br />\n打人勁契弟<br />\n亂吠 冇得扎<br />\n成隊去打後生仔<br />\n亂射 太多發<br />\n樓上叫我再準啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【亂咁打人】（打開蚊帳）<br />\n<br />\n亂咁打人 亂咁打人<br />\n亂棍扑 亂棍扑<br />\n記者都要打埋 訓低都照打埋<br />\n冇皇法 冇皇法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【全犯法】（刷牙歌）<br />\n<br />\n你被塔 佢被塔<br />\n香港警察全垃圾<br />\n小童成人全被塔<br />\n老人殘疾都應塔<br />\n你被殺 佢被殺<br />\n差佬攞炮胡亂殺<br />\n青年兒童全射殺<br />\n警棍胡椒加膠彈<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1212817\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1212817</a>"},{"pid":"eb06bdf0bd1501c062aa649002b91c5e85b42244","tid":1540481,"uid":254838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:01:27.000Z","msg":"奶媽生個毅進仔<br />\n人自閉<br />\n做隻龜<br />\n奶媽呢個毅進仔<br />\n條鳩好細"},{"pid":"60103883bb7aa5f715ffee7ce8597d61c46dbd9e","tid":1540481,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8528431eb674848b6755b158e512ed4861c5751b","tid":1540481,"uid":156902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:36:30.000Z","msg":"&lt;&lt;有班警察毅進仔&gt;&gt;<br />\n有班警察毅進仔    <br />\n人又廢    又要威<br />\n有班警察弱智仔<br />\n做狗乞米<br />\n<br />\n請各位番唱 再放上ig / fb / Snapchat story<br />\n要唱到幼稚園都識 就好似&lt;&lt;大笨象揸支槍去打仗&gt;&gt;、&lt;&lt;one more two more，屎忽大個菠蘿&gt;&gt;，等等<br />\n<br />\n唱到街知巷聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唱到班黑警有幻聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n瘋狂洗佢哋腦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n香港人 加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:05:49.000Z","msg":"呢個version一定要人人識唱，唱到小朋友都識！！！！<br />\n<br />\n等班仆街係呢個社會抬唔起頭做人。"},{"pid":"9d18074124501eaf948fb0cd1a7c9d2a832ab1b2","tid":1540481,"uid":238301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a838f705c667bdce475893acf4af0cc265d979","tid":1540481,"uid":116390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:07:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得食屎乞米岩音d"},{"pid":"2059343dda9a18a251a2ba212dcbff456fc27f27","tid":1540481,"uid":253329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T22:05:40.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥做特首<br />\n唔做野  等退休<br />\n五大訴求你要知<br />\n缺一 不可<br />\n<br />\n有班差佬發左癲<br />\n亂咁打  爆晒缸<br />\n呢班差佬等天收<br />\n禍及 妻兒"},{"pid":"619fc58ce946d0532804e788ffb9f2355eaff6ae","tid":1540481,"uid":156902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:01:15.000Z","msg":"識唱唒未呀！？"}]}